{
  "stem": "2804.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So half the time, we were filled with smoke or we weren't.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it was cold.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were there about 2 months, 2 and 1/2 months.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We got there in January of '45.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't see any of the townsfolk that day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the few days following that, very well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They seemed to accept us, the people that were there, because we-- we still would get up, and we would do calisthenics, and we would march and walk around the town.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as I said, in the snow and the mud, it was cold.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't think I've ever been so cold.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not very much.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We tried to just amuse ourselves, and, as I said, walk around the countryside.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There really wasn't too much to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were just sitting there waiting for something to happen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'45, January of 1945.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew that there was fighting going on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, that's-- no, we didn't know of anything else.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were just waiting for orders to do something or to go somewhere.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The beginning of March-- the-- around March, our colonel came up to us and said that our unit would be getting ready to leave, that they had gotten orders for us to get together.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they sent the trucks up, and we put all our equipment in.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We always went with our own footlockers and our bedrolls and our cots went with us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We started to head south into-- in France.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember in the beginning of April, when we did open up our hospital, we were always out in the field.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were an evacuation hospital.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
